1. Requirements
=%=%=%=%=%=%=%=

 - Android 1.5 or higher


2. Features
=%=%=%=%=%=

 - Watch the playlist of MpgX
 - Queue TV
 - Pause/Stop/Skip/... control of the music player using your Android phone



3. Installing
=%=%=%=%=%=%=

 - adb install MpgX-G1.apk


4. Bug reports
=%=%=%=%=%=%=%

Please send bug reports to: zillode@zillode.be

If you make any changes to the source, please mail me the 'diff -u' of the file(s) changed, and also why were the changes needed.



